Subject: Re: [T2] Mysterious Post-Ignition Sounds

Sounds like the shaft the bendix gear rides on is gummy. remove the starter,
clean the shaft and re-lube with a light coat of good grease and then
re-install. That's what fixed the same problem for me.

Dave

